header
    #logo
      a(href="/signup")
        img.logo_img(src="assets/images/which_method_logo.png", alt="", aria-label="Left Align")
    #menu

.col-md-6
  .row
    .col-sm-12
      h1 
        span(lang='en') SIGN UP*for WhichMethod
        span(lang='es') Inscríbase a WhichMethod
    .col-sm-12
      form.form(name='form', ng-submit='register(form)', novalidate='')
        .form-group(ng-class='{ "has-success": form.name.$valid && submitted,\
        "has-error": form.name.$invalid && submitted }')

        .form-group(ng-class='{ "has-success": form.email.$valid && submitted,\
        "has-error": form.email.$invalid && submitted }')
          h3 
            span(lang='en') Email
            span(lang='es') Correo Electrónico
          input.form-control(type='email', name='email', ng-model='user.email', required='', mongoose-error='')
          p.help-block(ng-show='form.email.$error.email && submitted')
            | Doesn't look like a valid email.
          p.help-block(ng-show='form.email.$error.required && submitted')
            | What's your email address?
          p.help-block(ng-show='form.email.$error.mongoose')
            | {{ errors.email }}

        .form-group(ng-class='{ "has-success": form.password.$valid && submitted,\
        "has-error": form.password.$invalid && submitted }')
          h3 
            span(lang='en') Password
            span(lang='es') Contraseña
          input.form-control(type='password', name='password', ng-model='user.password', ng-minlength='3', required='', mongoose-error='')
          p.help-block(ng-show='(form.password.$error.minlength || form.password.$error.required) && submitted')
            | Password must be at least 3 characters.
          p.help-block(ng-show='form.password.$error.mongoose')
            | {{ errors.password }}

        div
          button.btn.btn-default.btn-lg.btn-login(type='submit')
            span(lang='en') Register User
            span(lang='es') Registrar

          = ' '
          a.btn.btn-default.btn-lg.btn-register(href='/login')
            span(lang='en') Log in
            span(lang='es') Ingresa
          br
          br
          a.btn.btn-primary(data-toggle='collapse', ng-click="guestSignin()", aria-expanded='false', aria-controls='collapseExample')
            span(lang='en') Start as Guest User
            span(lang='es') Ingresar como Usuario Invitado
            br
        div
            br
            h5 
              span(lang='en') <mark>* By signing up you agree to WhichMethod.org's Privacy Policy</mark>
              span(lang='es') <mark>*Al inscribirse usted está de acuerdo con la Política De Privacidad de WhichMethod.org.</mark>
            br
            br
.col-md-6
  ul
    h4  
        span(lang='en') SIGN UP TODAY
        span(lang='es') INSCRÍBASE HOY
        h6 
          span(lang='en') There are two ways to use WhichMethod: <u>Registered Users</u> will receive up to 2 emails and will be able to save and email copy of Recommendations. <u>Guest Users</u> will be able to print recommendations, but must Register to email save.
          span(lang='es') Hay dos maneras para usar WhichMethod: <u>Usuario Registrado:</u> recibirá hasta 2 correos electrónicos y podrá salvar y recibir sus recomendaciones por correo electrónico. <u>Usuario Invitado:</u> podrá imprimir las recomendaciones pero para recibirlas por correo electrónico tiene que registrase.
    br
    h4 
        span(lang='en') ANSWER THE QUESTIONS
        span(lang='es') RESPONDA LAS PREGUNTAS
        h6 
          span(lang='en') WhichMethod asks questions about your medical history, preferences and priorities and sexual behavior in <kbd>Spanish</kbd> and <kbd>English</kbd>.
          span(lang='es') WhichMethod hace preguntas sobre su historia médica, preferencias y prioridades, historia sexual en <kbd>español</kbd> y en <kbd>inglés</kbd>.
    br
    h4 
        span(lang='en') GET RECOMMENDATIONS
        span(lang='es') RECIBA SUS RECOMMENDACIONES
        h6 
          span(lang='en') WhichMethod identifies birth control methods that are <u>effective</u>, <u>safe</u> and <u>fit your needs</u>. Please share Recommendations with your doctor.
          span(lang='es') WhichMethod identifica métodos anticonceptivos que sean <u>seguros, efectivos</u> y <u>adecuados para su estilo de vida</u>. Por favor comparta sus recomendaciones con su doctor.
    br
